remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 当它们被引发时<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件会传递的实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs>到关联的事件的处理程序。  
  
 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A>属性可以获取新的音频级别输入时<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.AudioLevelUpdated?displayProperty=nameWithType>引发事件。  
  
 `AudioLevel`属性<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>类提供的语音识别引擎的音频输入的当前级别。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 下面的示例将添加到事件处理程序<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>对象。 处理程序将输出到控制台的新音频级别。  
  
 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs> 派生自 <xref:System.EventArgs>。  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  
  
// Initialize the SpeechRecognitionEngine object.   
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  
  
  // Add an event handler for the AudioLevelUpdated event.  
  sre.AudioLevelUpdated += new EventHandler<AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs>(sre_AudioLevelUpdated);  
  
  // Add other initialization code here.  
}  
  
// Write the audio level to the console when the AudioLevelUpdated event is raised.  
void sre_AudioLevelUpdated(object sender, AudioLevelUpdatedEventArgs e)  
{  
  Console.WriteLine("The audio level is now: {0}.", e.AudioLevel);  
}  
  
```
